text: Has to be Europa. Bigger ocean than the Earth’s. Tidal heating deep below. Radiation and convection-driven chemistry in the ice crust. Bob Ballard and James Cameron have nothing on this!

text: I’ve been in love with Jupiter since I was a kid. Did “the flora/fauna of Jupiter,” based on creating a taxonomy from ACH’s Meeting w/Medusa, for my 7th grade science project. Monitored changes in the Great Red Spot with CCDs for my astronomy lab class in college.
